
#require no-eden


  $ configure modern
  $ enable rebase

Simple case:
  $ newrepo simple
  $ drawdag << 'EOS'
  >     Y
  >     |
  > X   B
  >  \ /
  >   A
  > EOS
  $ hg debugmakepublic $A::$B
  $ hg rebase -b $Y -d $X
  rebasing d2ed191ef6cc "Y"
  $ tglog
  o  089ea1cc331c 'Y'
  │
  o  bacc19fa7254 'X'
  │
  │ o  112478962961 'B'
  ├─╯
  o  426bada5c675 'A'
  

Rebasing public commits:
  $ newrepo publiccommits
  $ drawdag << 'EOS'
  > C
  > |
  > B X
  > |/
  > A
  > EOS
  $ hg debugmakepublic $A::$C
  $ hg rebase -b $C -d $X
  nothing to rebase from 26805aba1e60 to bacc19fa7254
